## ヒストグラム {#sec-Histogram}

-   $D=Reform$ ごとに以下を表示


::: {.panel-tabset}

### R



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
Data_R |> 
  mutate(Reform = factor(Reform)) |> 
  ggplot(
    aes(
      x = Size,
      fill = Reform,
      group = Reform
      )
    ) +
  geom_histogram(
    aes(y=..density..),
    alpha=0.5,
    position='identity'
    ) +
  theme_bw()
```

